442
00:38:15,190 --> 00:38:18,990
I think you came to get me, but I don't know why.

443
00:38:22,450 --> 00:38:24,800
Does it have anything to do with this?

444
00:38:26,290 --> 00:38:28,390
I guess you could say that.

445
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:34,430
We found an antibody in you.

446
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:38,070
We have to check and see if that antibody is useful.

447
00:38:38,070 --> 00:38:43,380
Even if we have to let you get bitten by an infected, if necessary.

448
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:09,390
Don't shoot!

449
00:39:10,530 --> 00:39:11,720
What?

450
00:39:11,720 --> 00:39:15,200
Didn't you just hear a gunshot?

451
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:20,650
